### Base controller request template
# 说明:
# 1. 这里是按照 athena-framework 的 `IController` 契约整理的通用测试骨架。
# 2. 复制到具体实体请求文件后，只需要改 `resourcePath` 和请求体字段即可。
# 3. `page` / `pageSearch` 都保留，方便按需测试分页和搜索接口。
# 4. `sorts` 格式是 `field:asc|desc`，`queries` 格式是 `field:value:typeCode`。

@apiPrefix = /aiEngine
@resourcePath = /api/v1/ai/meta/internal/provider
@id = 1
@page = 1
@size = 10
@sorts = id:desc
@queries = id:1:1
@contentType = application/json;charset=UTF-8
@acceptJson = application/json

### 1. 新增
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### 2. 全量更新
PUT {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/{{id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### 3. 局部更新
PATCH {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/{{id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### 4. 软删除
DELETE {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/{{id}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 物理删除
DELETE {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/physical/{{id}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 分页查询（GET）
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}?page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sorts={{sorts}}&queries={{queries}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 分页搜索（POST /_search）
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/_search
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "page": {{page}},
  "size": {{size}}
}

### 8. 按 ID 查询
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}{{resourcePath}}/{{id}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
